nodes.text: The Coruscant-Dantooine hyperlane was an ancient hyperlane that ran from Coruscant, the galactic capital, to Dantooine, in the Outer Rim Territories, from the period of the Great Hyperspace War until the New Sith Wars.

Beginning at the Core Worlds' Coruscant system, the hyperlane traversed through the Panto system, the Colonies' Palanhi system, passing through the Inner Rim and Expansion Region into the Mid Rim's Vicondor and Iridonia system, and then into the Outer Rim's Ord Cantrell, Dartibek, Ord Biniir, Ord Trasi, and Neka systems, before terminating in the Dantooine system.
